    <title>hexo踩坑合集</title>
    <url>/readmeh.github.io/2021/01/11/hexo%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo自身出错"><a href="#hexo自身出错" class="headerlink" title="hexo自身出错"></a>hexo自身出错</h1><h2 id="hexo报错-YAMLException-can-not-read-a-block-mapping-entry-a-multiline-key-may-not-be-an-implicit-key-at-line-7-column-1"><a href="#hexo报错-YAMLException-can-not-read-a-block-mapping-entry-a-multiline-key-may-not-be-an-implicit-key-at-line-7-column-1" class="headerlink" title="hexo报错 YAMLException: can not read a block mapping entry; a multiline key may not be an implicit key at line 7, column 1"></a>hexo报错 YAMLException: can not read a block mapping entry; a multiline key may not be an implicit key at line 7, column 1</h2><a id="more"></a>

<p>该错误出现原因大多为<code>: </code>没有加空格，这个错误可以出现在hexo的任何配置文件中如:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>  站点配置文件:_config.yml <img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2021/01/11/s8d5TI.png" alt="站点配置文件" style="zoom:50%;"></p>
</li>
<li><p>  主题配置文件:themes/next/_config.yml;</p>
</li>
<li><p>文章:source/_posts/hello-world.md;<img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2021/01/11/s8d40A.png" alt="s8d40A.png"></p>
<p>  <strong>一定要注意文章<code>tags: </code>后面虽然换行了，但也要有空格</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
